videos.description: Jaime Echenique falls down while defending a pick-and-roll, but is still able to get back on his feet in time to block Martins Igbanu at the bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wichita State’s Echenique gets the block at the rim) 2020// ESHEET

videos.headline: Wichita State's Echenique gets the block at the rim

videos.description: With 3.3 seconds on the clock and the game tied 51-51, Tulsa inbounds the ball and Elijah Joiner throws up a 3-pointer at the buzzer to knock off No. 23 Wichita State 54-51.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Tulsa’s Joiner sinks game-winning 3 to upset Wichita State) 2020/02/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tulsa's Joiner sinks winning 3 to upset Wichita State
